title: Sub-Culture
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sandwich place that offers a selection of vegan choices including whole wheat bread, daiya cheese, tofutti, nayonaise, house-made chipotle nayo and thousand island dressing. Has Wi-Fi, full bar, and large patio. The vegan Bangkok sandwich consists of wheat bread, marinated tempeh, nayo, carrots, romaine, pickles and a sweet chili sauce. Delivery is by bike.
